Motivation behind our project:
 As International students we pay a lot towards tuition and other
mandatory fees.
 We were curious to know the breakdown of the student fee structure
and also study the need for increase in the fee trend over the years.
3
Dataset used:
 Current Tuition Rates: http://www.odu.edu/admission/costs-
tuition/tuition/tuition-rates
 Archived Tuition Rates (back to 2004):
http://www.odu.edu/admission/costs-tuition/tuition/tuition-
rates/archived-rates
 Tuition rates of few public and private universities.
4
What-Why-How framework:
What: Data- Tables(Items and Attributes)- Static
What: Data Types- Categorical and Quantitative
Why: Actions Analyze- Discover, Present
Why: Actions Search- Browse, Explore
Why: Actions Query- Identify, Compare
Why: Targets All Data- Trends, Outliers
5
What-Why-How framework:
How: Encode Arrange- Express, Separate, Order, Align, Use(Google Maps,VA)
How: Encode Map- Color
How: Manipulate Change, Select, Navigate
How: Facet Juxtapose
How: Reduce Filter
